data.description: Welcome to 190 Panola Rd! Situated on 20 beautiful and private wooded acres sits a 1,820 SF manufactured home that has so much to offer! The interior features a foyer entrance, large living room with fireplace, separate dining room, and huge laundry room with washer, dryer, and utility sink. The kitchen is impressive with a commercial-grade stainless stove with hood vent, double oven, griddle, and flat-top! a chef's dream! There is a pantry with space for vegetables, fruits, canned goods, and snacks galore. Plenty of cabinet space, a breakfast bar, stainless refrigerator, and more makes the kitchen the heart of this home for sure. The master suite features an en suite bathroom with upgraded walk-in tile shower, two sinks, and walk-in closet. There are two secondary bedrooms and full bath down the hall giving privacy for the master. Outside the home you have a expanded front porch with gazebo, an enclosed porch/sunroom off the back of the home, a fenced in yard for pets, carport, two sheds, and a larger storage shed with power that could even become a tiny home/in-law suite. The potential at this property is endless! Call to schedule your own personal tour today!
